msg: GERONIMO-362. You can specify implemented-interface elements with additional interfaces the ConnectionFactory implementation class implements.  These will be implemented by the proxy you get from jndi.  For instance, it the ra-declared interface is javax.jms.ConnectionFactory, you might specify javax.jms.QueueConnectionFactory and javax.jms.TopicConnectionFactory
